---
title: Herby Lamb & Roast Beetroot Salad with Caramelised Onion & Mayo
description: It's roast lamb, but not as you know it! We're using our flavourful and earthy herb and mushroom seasoning to lift succulent
lamb rump to new heights. With a generous helping of roasted veggies, it's all you need to create a nutritious meal that's fit for
even the fussiest eaters.
